snippet.textDisplay:
This is my opinion below.. DON'T TAKE IT OFFENSIVE!

Legend:- Late Amjad Sabri
Singer of the year:- Noori and QB
Rising Singer:- Rachel Viccagi
Debut Singer( For Coke Studio ):- Momina Mustehsan
Song at the Last(not bad):- Bholay Bhalay
Coke Studio Overall Ratings this season:- 8.4
Last Season:- 8.9

My top 10:-
  1- Jhalliya
  2- Paar Chanaa De
  3- Sab Jag Soye
  4-Shamaan Pai Gaiyaan
  5- Rang
  6- Uddi Jaa
  7- Ala Baali
  8- Lagi Bina
  9- Tera Woh Pyar
10- Laung Gawacha (Only QB part)

Brief Description:- Wish it could play all year... Wanted More.
